
hb_4mike Finds depths associated with specified potential temperatures.

Usage:  hb_4mike filename_root(s)  [-D<dirname>] [-E<file_extent>] [-L<theta_level_file>]

  List of filenames MUST be first argument!
   [-L] : optional file of theta levels 
   [-D] : specifies directory for input files (default is current directory) 
            ex: -D../data/ 
   [-E] : specifies input_file extent (default is no extent)
            ex: -E.dat -h help...... prints this message. 


